  "denoised_question": "<denoised_question>Megan and Hana raced their remote control cars for 100 m. Megan's car traveled at an average speed of 5/4 m/s. Hana's car finished 5 seconds before Megan's. What was the average speed of Hana's car?</denoised_question>",
